Mary shrugged her shoulders but took the glass submissively and calling the nurse began giving the medicine. The child screamed hoarsely. Prince Andrew winced and, clutching his head, went out and sat down on a sofa in the next room. 
He still had all the letters in his hand. Open- ing them mechanically he began reading. The old prince, now and then using abbreviations, wrote in his large elongated hand on blue pa- per as follows :
